data.description: Discover this charming home in the heart of Hixson, offering unparalleled convenience to local schools, shopping centers, and dining establishments. This updated property boasts three bedrooms, including a master suite on the main floor. The fully finished basement, complete with a walkout covered porch, serves as a versatile space, ideal for a fourth bedroom or additional living area. This home showcases numerous upgrades and eco-friendly features, low-E insulated windows, and energy-efficient heat pump. The interior has been thoughtfully renovated with new flooring in the kitchen and basement, fresh paint throughout, and a stylishly remodeled full bathroom. Set on a spacious fenced-in lot, the property offers a serene outdoor oasis. Relax on the delightful screened porch, which overlooks a lush backyard featuring a charming firepit, perfect for entertaining guests or cultivating your own garden sanctuary. The bright kitchen with a cozy breakfast dining area provides seamless access to the screened porch, creating a seamless blend of indoor-outdoor living. Additionally, the home includes a convenient two-car garage with an automatic door opener, offering ample storage space for your belongings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this inviting home your own!
